## Problem 2 – Count Even Numbers from 1 to 10
i = 1
count = 0

while i <= 10:

    if i % 2 == 0:
        count = count + 1

    i = i + 1

print(count)

Output:

5

## Problem 3 – Sum of Numbers from 1 to 5
i = 1
sum = 0

while i <= 5:
    sum = sum + i
    i = i + 1

print(sum)

